
  AutoTweetNG - Facebook Authorization App
  ========================================
  
  Installation - STEP BY STEP TUTORIAL
  ------------------------------------
  
  How to AutoTweet from Your Own Facebook App
  *******************************************
  http://www.extly.com/how-to-autotweet-from-your-own-facebook-app.html#/prerequisites
	
  1. Prerequisites

    - AutoTweetNG Free (*) or PRO v6
      http://www.extly.com/autotweet-ng-pro.html
    - A Facebook account
    - A site with SSL support (E.g. Facebook's Heroku site)

 
	* Previous tutorial
	How to AutoTweet from Joomla in 5 minutes
	http://www.extly.com/how-to-autotweet-in-5-minutes-from-joomla.html

	About SSL & Facebook
    http://www.sourcecoast.com/jfbconnect/docs/common-support-questions/ssl-certificates-for-facebook
    
   2. Let's create a Facebook App
  
   https://developers.facebook.com/apps
   Create New App
   
   3. Now, you have your own:
   
   App ID
   App Secret
   
   4. From AutoTweetNG, unzip facebook_server_auth_app.zip
      Copy the files to your hosting,
      Manually, verify the Facebook App site,
      For example: https://app.extly.com/Facebook-App/ 	
  
   5. Please, fill App Id, App Secret, and Canvas Page; and 
   continue with the authorization steps (check 1ยบ tutorial).
   
